properties.Description: Annual community event to pull White Sweetclover in the Copper Basin
CRWP helped establish a CWMA in Copper Basin in 2015 to help control or eradicate priority invasive plants.
properties.Partners: Ahtna, Inc., BLM, CRWP, Wrangell St. Elias National Park & Preserve, USFWS
properties.Species: Bird Vetch, White Sweetclover, Narrowleaf Hawksbeard, Oxeye Daisy
